CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 30, 1958, pg. 32 reads: "Dangerous Pros - Four of the most highly regarded professionals in country take time out from a practice session to pose for our Courier photographer. Left to right are Charley Sifford, Joe Kennedy, Newark, N.J.; Clifton Harrington, Fort Campbell, Ky., and Ted Rhodes, defending UGA professional champion. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Charley Sifford, Joe Kennedy wearing Blue Elms Golf Club hat, Clifton Harrington, and Ted Rhodes, crouched down holding outstretched putters, North Park golf course for UGA tournament
